Pyrl How It Works About Security FAQ Blog For Retailers Contact Us SIGN UP SIGN IN Sign Up Sign In Welcome to the Pyrl Blog Data Democracy – When Innovation Builds Privacy and Trust, Everyone Wins Sep , A window of opportunity exists for consumers to get in the driver’s seat of their most valuable information, and put trust and value back where it read more Welcome to the Economy: Meet Pyrl Jun , Mistrust defines more than ever: socially, politically, economically — until now, there’s been no platform that provides the technology and business model to return trust to the consumer business read more Our story Jun 1, The origin of Pyrl began in , when I lost my dad to cancer… read more CONTACT US Alexander Bell Drive Suite Columbia, MD Subscribe to our mailing list to stay informed about Pyrl Leave this field empty if you re human: FAQ Technology Terms Privacy FAQ TECHNOLOGY TERMS PRIVACY Follow Follow Follow Follow We use cookies to for specific purposes as outlined in our Privacy Policy including to collect overall site statistics, and to maintain your session when you log into our Ok Privacy policy   Security - Pyrl How It Works About Security FAQ Blog For Retailers Contact Us SIGN UP SIGN IN Sign Up Sign In How Pyrl Protects Your Information Encryption & Storage We encrypt all your data, and no one (not even Pyrl employees) can see your transaction data, unless you grant temporary permission, for instance, in order for us to address a support request that you Pyrl uses security (256-bit SSL encryption) for all our interactions with This is the same security level and method used when you connect directly to your financial Pyrl also encrypts your data when it is stored in our database (“encryption ”). This means that even if we had an intruder, they would not be able to make any sense of your sensitive Going beyond the usual protections Pyrl’s security design prevents even our own staff from the ability to see your transaction The connection to all sensitive information is separately encrypted using your password, and stored This means that no one but you can ever link your name or identity to your For this reason, you may be asked to your password if you want to view your This also means that if you forget your password, you will need to any debit credit cards you’ve registered, in order to and these For more technical details, see Account Protection In addition to the above data protections on your account and transactions, you are also always in control of your Pyrl This includes the ability to or fully delete your account anytime you wish, as well as to request a secure download of your account Responsible Disclosure In order to perform our comittment to convey your data privacy directives to the businesses you’ve selected, retailers require that we verify you have appointed Pyrl to do We do this using the initials you enter when you sign They also need enough information to find you in their systems, so that your privacy requests can be Pyrl provides retailers with a secure API to acomplish We only provide each retailer with the minimum information needed to corrctly locate each individual in their Technical note: How can Pyrl really keep my data that secure? In traditional Chinese medicine, acupuncture heals many health conditions by restoring biological energy that continuously circulates through your This energy, Qi (pronounced ‘chee’), follows pathways called meridians that are associated with organ systems in your When a pathway is blocked, the affected system experiences stress and develops disease, illness, and As acupuncture needles are placed in precise locations associated with the blocked meridian, your normal energy flow is restored, allowing the body to use its inherent ability to Medical acupuncture targets areas where acupuncture needles can stimulate peripheral The nerves then send messages to the brain, which in turn releases compounds called As endorphins bind to opiate receptors, they produce a Researchers have found several other ways that acupuncture produces therapeutic For example, the treatment affects brain chemistry, triggering beneficial neurotransmitters or Another mechanism of action was illustrated when acupuncture brought pain relief to a group of adults with knee By taking functional MRIs before and after acupuncture treatments, researchers were able to show improved connectivity between areas of the SCHEDULE NOW What should I expect during an acupuncture session? Medical acupuncture administered by a acupuncturist at our The needles used during acupuncture are different from those used for medical Acupuncture needles are , flexible, and tapered, qualities that allow them to slide smoothly into the targeted In most cases, patients don’t feel anything as the needle is After the needle reaches the appropriate depth, you may feel a dull ache or tingling During an acupuncture session, your acupuncturist at Palo Alto Mind Body may manipulate the needles, twirling them or transmitting a electrical current through Throughout your acupuncture session, you should not experience pain or Sessions typically range from minutes, depending on your particular condition and The course of treatment may also depend on your health history and factors such as diet and Regardless of specific your particular lifestyle choices, both traditional Chinese medicine and the western scientific evidence have shown medical acupuncture to be highly effective against key metal and physical What health conditions may benefit from acupuncture? Medical acupuncture is being used to relieve pain caused by a variety of health For example, treatment guidelines developed by the American College of Physicians recommend acupuncture for treating chronic lower back The World Health Organization publishes a list of diseases and conditions that are proven to effectively treated with A few examples from the list include: Allergic rhinitis Depression A headache Facial pain Knee pain Chronic gastritis Neck and back pain Tennis elbow Sprains In addition to the conditions above, the acupuncturist at Palo Alto Mind Body also specializes in treating: Migraines Fatigue Insomnia Repetitive stress injuries Sports injuries If you’d like to consider acupuncture or if you have questions about whether it may benefit your health problem, call Palo Alto Mind

년까지 EU 전체 육지와 바다의 % 를 보호 지구로 지정 예정 유럽 연합 집행위원회는 동식물종의 감소를 막고 기후 변화를 해결하기 위해 년까지 EU 육지와 바다의 % 이상을 보호할 것이라고 했습니다 . 생물 다양성 전략은 3 월말에 발표될 예정이었으나 코로나 바이러스로 인해 발표가 지연됐고 , 이번에 발표되었습니다 . 발표된 년 비전에 따르면 EU 는 연간 최소 억 유로의 예산을 투입해 생태계를 복원하고 보호할 예정입니다 . 향후 년 동안 모든 EU 농지의 4 분의 1 을 유기농으로 바꾸고 농업 생태를 장려함으로써 농업 부문을 변화시키는 조치를 포함합니다 . 농업은 EU 의 생물 다양성을 손실시키는 원인 중 하나입니다 . 위원회는 이 전략이 EU 가 로부터 회복하는 데 “ 중요한 요소 ” 가 될 것이라고 말했다 . 과학자들은 전염병 발생 빈도가 증가하는 것은 생물 다양성 상실 , 삼림 벌채 , 서식지 파괴 및 야생 동물 불법 거래와 관련이 있다고 말합니다 . ICRP 는 생물 다양성을 보호하고 복원하는 것이 농업 , 어업 및 관광과 같은 여러 부문에 긍정적인 경제적 영향을 미칠 수 있으며 국가가 경제 영향으로 인해 감당할 때 일자리 창출을 촉진할 수 있다고 주장했다 . ( 중략 ) 원문보기 https: www.climatechangenews.com 2020 05 20 eu-plans-protect-30-land-seas-2030-biodiversity   따뜻해진 히말라야로 위험에 처해진 네팔 주민들 빈 진흙 오두막으로 점철된 울퉁불퉁 한 고원의 히말라야에서 탈출이 시작되었습니다 . Dhye 마을에서 농작물은 짤막하고 줄기는 죽었고 물이 부족합니다 . 유일한 학교는 몇 년 전에 문을 닫았습니다 . 식량이 줄어듦에 따라 대부분의 가족은 얼굴이없는 사람이 만든 적에게 쫓겨 떠났습니다 . 그들은 네팔의 기후 변화 로 인한 이민자이며 앞으로 더 많아질 것입니다 . 아직 마을에 남은 소남 치링 구룽씨는 “ 이 마을을 좋아지만 여기서는 더 이상 살아남을 수 없다 ” 라고 말했습니다 . 기후 변화는 히말라야 지역을 변화시켜 수자원에 의존하는 수백만의 남아시아인을 위험에 처하게 하고 네팔 북부의 세계 최고봉이있는 산 거주자이 좀더 낮은 고도에서 새로운 정착지를 찾게 합니다 . 1,500 마일의 히말라야에서 빙하가 녹고 있습니다 . 한때 채소 재배에 사용된 토지는 불모지가 되었습니다 . 야크 목축 자들은 동물의 방목지를 찾기 위해 고군분투하고 있다고 말합니다 . 기온이 상승하면서 말라리아와 뎅기열이 히말라야의 새로운 지역으로 퍼질 수 있다고 과학자들은 말하고 있으며 벌써 모기가 고지대에 나타나기 시작했습니다 . 원문보기 https: www.nytimes.com 2020 04 05 world asia nepal-himalayas-glacier-climate.html   탄소 가격 정책과 도구에 대한 정의 기후 변화 완화를 다루려면 광범위한 정책과 도구를 구현해야합니다 . 완화 목표를 달성하기 위한 비용 효율적인 도구로 간주되는 탄소 가격은 계속 증가하는 관심을 받고 있습니다 . 이론적으로 탄소 가격이 의미하는 바는 명확하지만 실제로 그것이 의미하는 바는 이해가 부족합니다 . 제 생각에 이것은 정책 입안자들이 탄소 가격 정책을 펼칠지 아니면 탄소 가격 측정 도구 (CPI) 를 구현할 것인지 평가할 때 약간 혼란스러운 것 같습니다 . 탄소 가격은 탄소 배출에 가격을 부과하는 정책입니다 . 이것은 또한 암시적 탄소 가격이라고도합니다 . 반면에 탄소 가격 책정 수단은 법적 및 제도적 인프라를 통해 구현되는 정책 수단으로 특정 산업 부문이나 기업에 탄소 배출 가격을 제시할 수 있습니다 . 이것은 명시적 탄소 가격이라고도 합니다 . 탄소 가격 정책이 시행되면 연료와 에너지 보조금을 없앨 것이므로 이 두 가지 개념은 관련이 있습니다 . 이는 탄소 배출 감소에 막대한 영향을 미칠 수 있지만 , 정책 수단을 지원하기 위해 인프라를 개발할 필요는 없습니다 . 즉 , 명시적인 탄소 가격을 제공하기 위해 CPI 가 필요하지 않습니다 . ( 중략 ) 원문보기 https: www.carbonpricingleadership.org blogs 2020 4 20 defining-carbon-pricing-policy-and-instruments   석탄 산업은 코로나 이후 회복되지 않을 전망 세계 석탄 산업은 전염병으로부터 “ 회복하지 않을 것 ” 이라고 업계 전문가들은 예측했다 . 위기는 신재생 에너지가 소비자들에게는 더 저렴하고 투자자들에게는 더 안전함이 입증 되었기 때문이다 . 화석 연료에서 멀어지면서 장기적인 변화가 가속화되고 여러 국가에서 발전소 폐쇄가 이루어졌다 . 년 이상 이어져 온 인류의 석탄 사용이 마침내 정점에 올랐다는 것이 증빙되고 있습니다 . 나머지 세기 동안 석탄이 지속적인 확장을 한다는 시나리오는 가능성이 낮습니다 . 전염병이 발생하기 전에도 기후 활동 강화 , 탈석탄 캠페인 및 저렴한 대안으로 인해 석탄 업계는 압박을 받았습니다 . 석탄 발전소 폐쇄로 석탄 광산 시장 가치가 수십억 달러 떨어졌으며 석탄 산업의 약점이 더욱 드러났습니다 . 전기 수요가 감소함에 따라 많은 석탄 설비가 가스 , 바람 및 태양보다 비싸기 때문에 석탄이 먼저 공급을 줄였습니다 . EU 에서는 화력 발전소의 석탄 수입이 최근 몇 달 동안 3 분의 2 로 급감하여 년 동안 볼 수 없었던 최저 수준에 도달했다 . 그 결과는 전세계에서도 느껴졌습니다 . 이번 주 미국 에너지 정보국 (US Energy Information Administration) 의 보고서는 미국이 올해 처음으로 석탄보다 재생 에너지로부터 더 많은 전력을 생산할 것이라고 예측했습니다 . 업계 분석가들은 미국 전력 생산량에서 석탄의 비중이 년 전 % 에서 5 년 만에 % 로 떨어질 것이라고 예측했습니다 . 도널드 트럼프의 " 석탄 발굴 " 캠페인 서약에도 불구하고 , 년 전 아이젠 하워 대통령직 이후 어느 때보다 업계에서 일자리 손실과 폐쇄가 더 많았습니다 . 그중 가장 최근에는 그레이트 리버 에너지 (Great River Energy) 가 노스 다코타 주에 기가 와트 열 발전소를 폐쇄하고 이를 풍력과 가스로 대체하려는 계획이 있었습니다 . ( 중략 ) 원문 : https: www.theguardian.com environment 2020 may 17 coal-industry-will-never-recover-after-coronavirus-pandemic-say-experts   재생에너지가 화석연료보다 경쟁 우위 보이는 중 IRENA(International Renewable Energy Agency) 의 신규 보고서에 따르면 , 재생에너지의 생산비가 화석 연료 기반의 신규 전력 플랜트보다 낮아지고 있습니다 . 년 새로 만들어진 재생에너지의 절반 이상이 가장 저렴한 신규 석탄 발전소보다도 낮은 비용에 전력을 생산할 수 있습니다 . 보고서에 따르면 새로운 재생 가능 발전 프로젝트가 기존의 석탄 화력 발전소를 점점 약화시키고 있습니다 . 평균적으로 , 새로운 태양광 발전 (PV) 과 육상 풍력 발전은 기존의 많은 석탄 공장을 운영하는 것보다 저렴하며 경매 결과는 이러한 추세가 가속화되고 있음을 보여줍니다 . 내년에는 최대 1,200 기가 와트 (GW) 의 기존 석탄 용량을 유지하는 게 새로운 태양광을 설치하는 것보다 비용이 더 많이들 수 있다고 보고서는 밝혔습니다 . 내년에 가장 비용이 많이 드는 의 석탄을 태양광 및 육상 풍력으로 교체하면 매년 최대 억 달러의 전력 시스템 비용을 절감하고 연간 배출량을 약 기가 톤 (Gt) 의 이산화탄소를 줄일 수 있습니다 . 이는 년 전 세계 이산화탄소 배출량의 5% 에 해당합니다 . 또한 전 세계 GDP 의 약 1% 에 해당하는 억 달러의 투자를 유도할 수 있습니다 . IRENA 의 프란체스코 라 카메라 (Francosco La Camera) 사무 총장은 “ 에너지 전환에서 중요한 전환점에 도달했으며 석탄 발전은 환경적으로나 경제적으로 정당화될 수 없다 ” 고 말했다 . 그는 또 “ 재생 가능 에너지는 점점 더 저렴한 신 전력 공급원이 되어 세계 경제를 자극하고 사람들을 다시 일할 수 있는 엄청난 잠재력을 제공하며 재생 에너지에 대한 투자는 안정적이고 비용효율적이며 매력적이며 일관되고 예측 가능한 수익을 제공하는 동시에 경제에 더 많은 혜택을 제공한다 ” 고 밝혔습니다 . 기술 , 규모의 경제 개선 , 공급체인 증가 및 개발자 경험 증가로 재생에너지 전기 생산 비용이 지난 년 동안 급격히 떨어졌습니다 . 년 이후 건설 비용은 태양광 발전이 % 로 가장 큰 비용 감소를 보였고 , 집중 솔라 발전 (CSP) 이 %, 지상 풍력 %, 해상 풍력 % 순이었습니다 . 태양광 및 풍력의 전력 생산비도 매년 하락했습니다 . 년 태양광 발전의 전기 비용은 % 감소하여 kWh 당 세계 평균 USD 에 도달했습니다 . 육상 및 해상 풍력은 각각 9% 감소하여 kWh 당 USD 및 USD 를 기록했습니다 . ( 중략 ) 원문보기 https: unfccc.int news renewables-beating-coal-competitors-on-cost   기후와 미국의 2 조 달러 지원금 패키지 상원은 수요일 오후 코로나 바이러스 전염병에 대한 대책으로 2 조 달러 규모의 경기 부양책에 투표하는데 , 기후 변화에 대한 대책은 혼재되어 있습니다 . 이 법안은 공화당과 트럼프 대통령이 추구한 전략 석유 예비비를 채우는 데 억 달러를 포함하지 않습니다 . 그러나 민주당이 추구한 풍력 및 태양 에너지에 대한 연방 세금 공제 연장또한 없습니다 . 항공사들이 요구한 억 달러 이상을 지원책도 없는 것으로 확인됐습니다 . 이 법안은 기후 변화 조항을 삽입하려는 노력을 시작한 5 일간의 격렬한 협상의 결과입니다 . 트럼프 대통령은 그러한 조항들을 포함한 모든 조치를 거부한다고 말했습니다 . 환경 및 재생 가능 에너 지 활동가들은 화석 연료와 재생 가능 에너지 부문이 서로 비겼다고 평가했습니다 . 시에라 클럽 (Sierra Club) 전무 이사 마이클 브런 (Michael Brune) 은 “ 민주당 지도자들은 석유 산업과 같은 오염 물질 대신에 노동자 , 가족 ,

FBAR for Expats explained | Expatfile US Expat Tax US Expat Taxes Explained Expat taxes for & digital nomad FBAR for expats FEIE Foreign Earned Income Exclusion Bona Fide Residence Test Physical Presence Test Foreign Housing Exclusion FTC Pricing Faq Blog Start FBAR for expats As a US expat, you may or may not know that on top of having to file your federal tax return every year, you may also have to file FinCen Form , or the “FBAR” as This article gives you an overview of the basics of complying with the FBAR rules, and covers what the FBAR entails, who needs to file, what needs to be reported, when the FBAR needs to be filed, and the consequences of not What is FinCEN Form (FBAR)? Since , the US requires citizens to file an informational report annually to disclose their foreign financial This report is known as FinCEN Form – Report of Foreign Bank and Financial Accounts (“FBAR”). This law was introduced to identify foreign financial accounts held by US persons in order to prevent offshoring of assets and Rest assured, Form is only for informational No tax will be imposed, but there are strict penalties for (see below). What foreign financial accounts need to be reported? The foreign financial accounts subject to FBAR include all checking, savings, and investment accounts, including most types of foreign pensions, but excluding mortgages and hedge Who needs to file a US FBAR? If you are an expat you most likely have a foreign account for your daily banking Expats are required to file an FBAR to report their financial interest in (i.e., ownership), or signature or other authority of an account located with a foreign financial The reporting requirement is triggered if the aggregate value of those foreign financial accounts exceed $10,000 at any time during the calendar All bank accounts, security accounts and retirement accounts need to be reported are subject to FBAR For example, if you have two bank accounts, each with a max balance of $5,000 during the year, then you need to disclose these accounts! When do you need to file FBAR as an expat? In the filing deadline for FBAR has been synchronized with the federal tax return The regular deadline for filing your FBAR is April , however, for expats an automatic extension to file your federal tax return is granted to June , and the FBAR deadline follows A further extension to file your federal tax return will also automatically be granted if you file for such an extension by June as an What are the penalties for not filing FinCen Form (US FBAR form)? If you haven’t filed FBAR, you could face serious penalties or even The penalties for not filing your FBAR could be substantially higher than penalties for not filing your federal US tax Civil law penalty The penalty for not filing your FBAR is $10,000 for each However, if the reason for not filing is found to be willful, the penalty is the greatest of $100,000 or % of the amount in the account for each Every year you are not filing your FBAR counts as a seperate Criminal law penalty If a criminal penalty is imposed, you can even get a fine of $250,000 and 5 years It can even get If you violate the FBAR requirement while violating another law (most of the times tax law) the penalties can even increase to $500,000 in fines and or years of Please be noted that in practice these FBAR violations are punished more mildly, but this is what the law provisions tell Where can I file my FBAR? You can your FBAR directly through the FinCen’s online filing Although anybody can file themself, Expatfile believes that this process can be more efficient and quicker if you have the right We will support this soon (not first June release). In the meantime, we can send you an email with very instructions to complete FBAR through BSA Filing . Read more here! Quote Business & Commercial Insurance Information Commercial Auto As a business owner, you need the same kinds of insurance coverages for the car you use in your business as you do for a car used for personal travel -- liability, collision and comprehensive, medical payments (known as personal injury protection in some states) and coverage for uninsured In fact, many business people use the same vehicle for both business and If the vehicle is owned by the business, make sure the name of the business appears on the policy as the "principal insured" rather than your This will avoid possible confusion in the event that you need to file a claim or a claim is filed against Whether you need to buy a business auto insurance policy will depend on the kind of driving you A good insurance agent will ask you many details about how you use vehicles in your business, who will be driving them and whether employees, if you have them, are likely to be driving their own cars for your While the major coverages are the same, a business auto policy differs from a personal auto policy in many technical Ask your insurance agent to explain all the differences and General Liability If you have a personal umbrella liability policy, there s generally an exclusion for Make sure you have sufficient auto liability Unfortunately for every business owner, the chances of getting sued have dramatically increased in the last General Liability insurance can prevent a legal suit from turning into a financial disaster by providing financial protection in case your business is ever sued or held legally responsible for some injury or General Liability pays losses arising from real or alleged bodily injury, property damage, or personal injury on your business premises or arising from your Broad Range of General Liability Protection Bodily Injury, including the cost of care, the loss of services, and the restitution for any death that results from injury Property Damage coverage for the physical damage to property of others or the loss of use of that property Operations provides liability protection (damages and legal expenses up to your policy s limit) if an injury ever resulted from something your company made or service your company provided Products Liability is a more specialized product liability insurance that protects your company against lawsuits from injury or accidents Contractual Liability extends to any liability you may assume by entering into a variety of contracts Other coverage includes: Reasonable Use of Force Borrowed Equipment Liquor Liability Vehicles (such as aircraft and watercraft) Fire, Lightning or Explosion Damage Water Damage Liability Protection Legal Defense Costs Medical Payments Personal Injury Advertising Injury and specialized liability protection for specific business types Workers Compensation Workers compensation laws were created to ensure that employees who are injured on the job are provided with fixed monetary This eliminates the need for litigation and creates an easier process for the It also helps control the financial risks for employers since many states limit the amount an injured employee can recover from an Workers Compensation Insurance is designed to help companies pay these As a protection for employees, most states require that employers carry some form of Workers Compensation Workers Compensation Insurance is not health Workers Compensation is designed specifically for injuries sustained on the In most states, if you have employees, you are required to carry Workers Compensation Even in states, it can be a very good idea, particularly if you have many employees, or if they are engaged in hazardous Do I need workers compensation insurance? Employers have a legal responsibility to their employees to make the workplace However, accidents happen even when every reasonable safety measure has been To protect employers from lawsuits resulting from workplace accidents and to provide medical care and compensation for lost income to employees hurt in workplace accidents, in almost every state, businesses are required to buy workers compensation Workers compensation insurance covers workers injured on the job, whether they re hurt on the workplace premises or elsewhere, or in auto accidents while on It also covers Workers compensation provides payments to injured workers, without regard to who was at fault in the accident, for time lost from work and for medi

For best results: First time baking please check often and Do NOT over bake Avoid using dark colored cookie sheets If you’re not eating your cookies shortly after they’re baked, remove them from the sheet and cool further on a wire rack DO NOT place cookies on a towel or paper product until fully cooled When using a commercial oven, drop the temperature degrees Please note that oven temperatures vary We d love to hear from you! Renozee™ Frequently asked questions (FAQs) × A note to our community regarding Learn more Contractors Contractors FAQs Frequently asked questions Most commonly asked questions by investment property owners and contractors For Contractors For Real Estate Investors About Renozee™ Renozee™ was built to enable both real estate investors and independent contractors to achieve the common goal of having a successful investment property In support of this common goal, we’ve created Renozee™, a mobile app that allows investors to post renovation projects and contractors to bid directly on those projects in real The Benefits of Renozee™ Winning work is crucial to building a thriving independent contracting business for home renovation Today’s independent contractors must find every opportunity to maximize their time and One of the best ways to do this is to utilize Renozee™. Some of the benefits of Renozee include: A more streamlined bidding process Helps to provide more competitive bids that are more likely to All competitors bids and profiles are visible to you (no sealed or hidden bids) so you can adjust your Helps to foster new relationships with real estate investors that lead to repeat business Track bidding communication and information all in one place Helps you to follow up on bid communication quickly Increases customer transparency No lead or monthly subscription fees of any kind Is there a fee for Independent Contractors to use the platform? Renozee™ is free to sign up, create a profile, select projects you are interested in, upload a portfolio, receive project notifications, discuss project details with customers, and bid on If you are awarded the project and you accept, we deduct a small % commission from the total bid amount paid out to We only make money if you win the job and complete the If the customer subsequently pays more than the original bid amount, we will also charge the project fee on any overage How does milestone payments work? Payments made out to contractors are based on milestone After a customer accepts your bid, you will be required to setup at least 1 milestone The customer will then be prompted to make the milestone payment which will be transferred to For example, a bathroom renovation project, demolition is typically the first For every milestone that is completed, the customer confirms and then releases those funds into your If there are other milestone tasks setup for the project, the customer will then be prompted to make the next milestone payment which will be transferred to How long does it take for me to receive payments? The first transaction takes approximately 7 business days and approximately business days after Our goal is to continue to work on shortening the payout Why does Renozee™ need my bank account information? We use your bank account information to submit customer payments to How does the financial transaction work? When a customer accepts a bid, they will be prompted to make a The funds are transferred to When the contractor successfully completes a milestone, and the customer confirms, the funds are released and disbursed into the contractors What if I need to go see the project site to gather additional information? In some cases, a site visit may be necessary, just be sure that the customer payments are received through the milestone payment system setup on the The milestone payment system was established to protect the contractor as well as the Completing the financial transaction off the platform will result in your account automatically being flagged and What if I m not winning any jobs? Don t give up, persistence is You may not win the job on your first bid Renozee™ makes it easy for you to your bid and submit a more competitive Renozee™ also on how to bid remodeling How can I win more jobs? Build a winning Along with your bid, customers will view your Ensure that license and insurance information are up to date, add quality photos of your past jobs, get reviews, and update every new skill that you Lastly, provide high quality bids that are detailed which include items like labor and What if I m selected for a project and upon the project site visit there is a "material" or significant difference in the project from what was listed in the project details? Variety: Baby eats a variety of textures and flavors, which may reduce picky eating later Less Expensive: Baby eats real No pricey jars, pouches, or blenders Family Meals: Baby is part of your family meal, eating with Dining Out: It’s easier to eat in restaurants as baby can eat whole Success: Babies are more likely to eat what you Fun! Babies enjoy touching, inspecting, and tasting a different flavors and Cons: Mess: When babies , it’s monumentally messy! Food Waste: broccoli that lands on the floor is not likely to be Gagging: Baby may gag in the first few weeks, though is less likely to gag later The traditional approach to feeding babies, where the parent is in total Foods served are typically puréed or Babies who are should be given the opportunity to eat on their own, with their fingers, by 9 months old (at which point you can transition away from ) Pros: Clean and tidy: You are in control of feeding and the mess is Less Time Consuming: You don’t need to cook or buy a lot of Less Waste: Most puréed food ends up in baby’s mouth or saved in the Cons: Dependency: Baby relies on you to eat, which you’ll need to transition away from around 9 months Oral development: Baby may have a harder time with textures later on, which can lead to prolonged gagging and preferences for soft Appetite Control: Baby has less of an opportunity to learn how to regulate their own appetite and to stop eating when feeling Nutrition: It’s easier to with purées, which can lead to an undesirable decrease in breast or bottle feeds (which are critical until your baby is months old). Picky Eating: Baby has less exposure to a variety of textures, which can lead to preferences for smooth Family Meals: Baby does not get to eat what the rest of the family eats and has less of an opportunity to learn by Expensive: Puréed baby food costs more per ounce than whole Environmental Impact: Processed baby food tends to have a larger carbon Pouches in particular are not environmentally friendly as they cannot be Less Babies can’t choose among foods, to touch and explore or Combo Feeding As the name indicates, a combination of and with finger As with exclusive , babies should be given the opportunity to by 9 months old to encourage Pros: Independence: Baby can practice some alongside being Less Mess: Not totally messy or totally clean Family Meals: Baby can join you at the table and eat some of what you Development: Baby gets to practice critical motor and oral development Variety: Babies can be exposed to a wide variety of textures and Cons: Confusion: Babies may not understand why sometimes they are and sometimes left to Appetite Control: Baby has less of an opportunity to learn how to regulate their own appetite and to stop eating when feeling Time & Mess: You are required to your child but also have to deal with the mess of some finger foods—a double whammy! Expanded Customer Service Provide your existing customers with expanded delivery options by taking advantage of Blue Fetch s courier Get immediate delivery quotes when you submit a request in our easy to use online courier What Do We Need From Our Building Supply Partners? Accurate Inventory Pricing It is vital to have the most pricing for all the building supplies that are available on the Blue Fetch web The majority of the time, our developers can set up automation to integrate with your existing inventory management If not possible, you will also have the ability to manually update pricing by importing a spreadsheet as Fast Order Confirmations When an order is routed to your location, you will receive your choice of an email, text, or phone call to notify you of a pending We ask that you confirm material availability by clicking an Approve Button in your vendor This will prompt a Blue Fetch driver to be routed to you for Expedited Order Fulfillment Delivering the customers building supplies quickly and accurately is our top To achieve this, we need your team to pull the materials as quickly as possible to be ready when our driver arrives for Blue Fetch Vendor Portal There s no need to purchase any hardware or Our simple web based vendor portal gives you access to everything you need to work with Blue Fetch! View and confirm all products for orders routed to your location with a couple of clicks Chat with the Blue Fetch support staff at any time View and manage all of the building materials you have available on the Blue Fetch web store Request Blue Fetch courier services and track delivery progression How do you start working with Blue Fetch? Blue Fetch is a service, but people are our most valuable The first step in this process is to meet with your dedicated SRM or Supplier Relationship The SRM will answer any questions you may have about working with us and confirm it makes sense for both parties to work Once it s determined to be beneficial for both of us to work together, we ll begin the simple implementation process: We ll complete all of the required paperwork to establish a purchase account with your business We ll get your account set up in our online vendor portal and give you a short tutorial on how to use the simple online system You ll need to determine what materials you will add to the Blue Fetch online These should be materials that are typically in stock and available right away since we are geared towards , same day We will need to work together to set up inventory management in our We have developers that can automate this process to make it easier for If automation is not possible, our techs can manually load the initial inventory information into our From there, it will be simple for you to make pricing updates as And that s it! From there, you will start receiving notifications if an order is routed to your Feel free to reach out to your SRM at any time for all questions or What does Blue Fetch look for in a partner? We re the BrooklineBots, Brookline s , female FTC BrooklineBots (BBots) ​We run the Brookline Robotics Initiative(BRI), a certified (c)(3) nonprofit! We are high school females in through grade at Brookline High We are devoted to developing the best possible robot for our competitions and furthering robotics in Brookline through the Brookline Robotics Initiative (BRI). We want to make robotics accessible to everyone, especially girls, to show that no matter who you are, you can do robotics! ​ ​Our team is divided into multiple sections including Build, Software, Fundraising, PR, Engineering Notebook, Brookline Teen Center Partnership, Elementary School Collaboration, BHS Robotics Club, Website , and more! Since our first season (2019-20), we ve been so grateful to qualify twice for states and win these awards: place Connect Award (6 times!) place Inspire Award place Motivate Award Compass Award (for our amazing coach, Adam Rizika!) Synesis | Synesis stops cooperation with Aleph Digital Fraud investigation launched Home Projects Startups News Jobs About us FAQ Partners Talents Contacts En Ru En All news Synesis stops cooperation with Aleph Digital Fraud investigation launched 1 November Synesis closed the Aleph The company’s experts did not reproduce the results demonstrated by Aleph Digital startup, and also found traces of fraudulent schemes in the team’s An investigation against Kirill Sancharov and his partners has been launched as the team is suspected of “ We believe that Kirill Sancharov is a serial IT fraudster who successfully replicates the scheme of attracting investments in breakthrough compression The outstanding results in the field of compression of incompressible files were obtained by him using trick The code is an obfuscation of existing PAQ family algorithms, ” comments Nikolai Ptitsyn , managing partner of Nikolai Ptitsyn and Kirill Sancharov (Aleph Digital) “ We believe that Aleph’s tricky applications simulate data compression in various ways, for example, by covertly writing source files to a local disk or to the The disclosure of this scheme was delayed due to the endless delay in transferring executable files and source codes to our experts for For months, Kirill postponed the transfer of materials under the pretext of the technology leak risk, “studying” at the Moscow Institute of Physics and Technology, health problems or persecution by third parties ,” continues Nikolai Despite the difficulties in accessing the source code for Aleph Digital’s products, Synesis experts were able to identify that they are simplified or rewritten versions of the algorithms of the PAQ family with open source codes and a GNU GPL The executable files were comparable in operating time and compression ratio with freely available archivers (PAQ-paq8pxd, ZPAQ). One of the versions of the archiver received from Kirill Sancharov exactly repeated the work of paq8pxd Attempts to confuse our experts were also made by providing some executable files demonstrating an “incredible” degree of Such programs have successfully reduced the size of files with data obtained from the MT number generator, which is unattainable for all compression algorithms available Surprisingly, they even compressed their own For example, by sequentially compression of a 1 GB file, you could come to about 7 Decompiling one of these versions showed that it hides a copy of the compressed file, and fills the archive with “garbage.” When unzipping, the copy was returned to its After Sancharov found out our expert’s testing methods, the Aleph Digital team made unsuccessful attempts to change the archiver operation In order to prevent the recurrence of fraud, we publish the composition of the Aleph Digital group, to which, in addition to Sancharov Kirill Vladimirovich (Kirill Sancharov, ), Konev Maxim Pavlovich, Shmelkov Andrei Nikolaevich, Skripkin Aleksandr Vladimirovich, Arkhipov Evgeny Sergeevich, Soldatov Aleksandr Vladimirovich, Liz Yuryevna, Agafonov The legal entities Aleph Digital (Aleph Digital, TIN ) and (TIN ) are associated with Kirill Synesis stops all joint activities with Kirill Sancharov and Aleph Digital startup, including in the joint company Synesis Projects Startups Jobs News About Us FAQ © Copyright All Rights   Synesis | Synesis прекращает сотрудничество со стартапом Aleph Digital Главная Проекты Стартапы Новости Вакансии О нас FAQ Клиент Соискатель Контакты Ru Ru En Все новости Synesis прекращает сотрудничество со стартапом Aleph Digital 1 ноября Synesis закрыл проект Эксперты компании не воспроизвели результаты, продемонстрированные стартапом Aleph Digital, а также обнаружили следы обманных схем в действиях Проводится расследование в отношении Кирилла Санчарова и его партнеров в связи с подозрением в « Мы считаем, что Кирилл Санчаров — серийный авантюрист и мошенник в сфере ИТ, успешно тиражирующий схему привлечения инвестиций в «прорывную» технологию «Выдающиеся» результаты в области «сжатия» несжимаемых файлов были получены им при помощи Исходный код является обфускацией существующих алгоритмов семейства PAQ» , — комментирует Николай Птицын , управляющий партнер Кирилл Санчаров (справа) «По нашему мнению, Aleph имитируют сжатие информации различными способами, например, путем скрытой записи исходных файлов на локальном диске или в Раскрытие этой схемы затянулось бесконечного затягивания передачи исполняемого и исходного кодов на тестирование нашим В течение месяцев Кирилл откладывал передачу материалов под предлогом риска утечки технологии, «обучением» в МФТИ, проблем со здоровьем или преследованием со стороны третьих лиц» , — продолжает Николай Несмотря на сложности с доступом к исходному коду разработок Aleph Digital, эксперты Synesis смогли выявить, что они представляют собой упрощенные либо переписанные версии алгоритмов известного семейства PAQ с открытыми «исходниками» и лицензией GNU Исполняемые же файлы были сопоставимы по времени работы
